{"an4.242:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.242 ","an4.242:0.2":"24. Kammavagga ","an4.242:0.3":"Sappurisanisamsasutta ","an4.242:1.1":"“Sappurisam, bhikkhave, nissaya cattaro anisamsa patikankha. ","an4.242:1.2":"Katame cattaro? ","an4.242:1.3":"Ariyena silena vaddhati, ariyena samadhina vaddhati, ariyaya pannaya vaddhati, ariyaya vimuttiya vaddhati—","an4.242:1.4":"sappurisam, bhikkhave, nissaya ime cattaro anisamsa patikankha”ti. ","an4.242:1.5":"Ekadasamam. ","an4.242:1.6":"Kammavaggo catuttho. ","an4.242:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","an4.242:2.1":"Sankhitta vitthara sonakayana, ","an4.242:2.2":"Sikkhapadam ariyamaggo bojjhangam; ","an4.242:2.3":"Savajjanceva abyabajjham, ","an4.242:2.4":"Samano ca sappurisanisamsoti. "}